    <h1>Documents &amp; Transcriptions</h1>
    <p>This page contains transcriptions and translations of key primary source documents, with the original German or Polish text alongside English translations.</p>

    <h2>German Restitution (Wiedergutmachung)</h2>
    <p>After emigrating to Israel, Herman pursued <em>Wiedergutmachung</em> (restitution/reparations) from West Germany for damages suffered during the Nazi persecution.</p>
